# Sum of proper divisors.
*divisor_sum(n as i64) returns i64
    s is 1
    i is 2
    while i * i <= n
        if n mod i equals 0
            s is s + i
            other is n / i
            if other neq i
                s is s + other
        i is i + 1
    if n equals 1
        return 0
    s

*main
    log divisor_sum(1)
    log divisor_sum(6)
    log divisor_sum(28)
    log divisor_sum(12)
